title: DMI Sports Black CricketPro Dartboard Cabinet | Designed for Arachnid 15.5” CricketPro 900, 800, 750, 650 Electronic Dartboards | Does Not Include Dartboard
description: Introducing the DMI Sports Cricket Pro Dartboard Cabinet, the perfect accompaniment for your Arachnid 15.5” Target Cricket Pro Model Electronic Dartboards, including the Cricket Pro 900, 800, 750 and 650. This cabinet is designed to fit these specific models, and it comes with two dedicated mounting hardware bolts to ensure easy installation. The cabinet is crafted with 12mm thick doors and deluxe steel hinges, providing durability and longevity for years of use. In addition, built-in dart holders can accommodate up to 12 darts, ensuring that your darts are always within easy reach. The extra large dartboard cabinet's assembled dimensions measure 24" L x 4" D x 35.4" H, providing ample space to house your dartboard while also adding an elegant touch to your game room or den. With its sleek design and sturdy construction, this dartboard cabinet is an excellent addition to any home game setup.
